E-10 THE POINT THAT REVERSING MUST BE NUMBER
E-11 THERE IS NOT SETTING CODE IN SETTING M/F
E-12 LOT ISN'T INPUT
E-13 L.T ISN'T INPUT
E-14 COEFFICIENT ISN'T INPUT
E-15 ADDRESS ISN'T INPUT
E-16 THE EFFECTIVE DATE IS THE PAST DAY
E-17 RAW MATERRIAL ADDRESS ISN'T INPUT
E-18 MACHINE NUMBER ISN'T INPUT
